message.body: Hi! Julie said you were coming to Philly for Penn homecoming?!!! Is that this Saturday? If so, I will join you guys! I haven't seen you in so long.
Hey! It's actually next weekend! I'm not sure yet if I'm even going to any actual homecoming events, but I'll be in Philly sat/sun. You're coming to Julie's bday party on sun, right??
Yes! Definitely. So either way I will see you there for sure
